{
  "stem": "17330.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 54.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were musicians and they played in Maastricht music for a living.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And somebody [INAUDIBLE] them in because he was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she was brought in too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we were there with the three of us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then the 12 days, the warden came and said to me, you have to go to the white house.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the white house was where the SS was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But before it all started that I left Amsterdam and all that, I said to my husband, if we are caught, I'll take the blame.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I'll say I'm pregnant and I'm nervous wreck and whatever.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we kept to that agreement.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Then when I came outside, there was a policeman with a motorcycle with the side [INAUDIBLE], a sidecar.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I had to put up a star, a David Star.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And there I went in the sidecar to [LAUGHS] the white house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And when I came there, there were three men there, three German.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they asked me I don't know how many questions, what I was doing and why I was there and all that business.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I should know I was not allowed to travel without papers and without a star and all that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] How do you feel?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I made all kind of excuses and they didn't say much.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then but when I went in that motorcycle, the policeman said to me, you must have regards for your husband.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, how come?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, he went this morning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he want me to tell you that he's OK.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "All right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then they drove me back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when I came back in the cell, then they-- after maybe 5 or 10 minutes the warden came back.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she said, you can go.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
